    <title>HyperXenon一键移植脚本</title>
    <url>/2025/01/18/HyperXenon%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hyper-Xenon-一键移植脚本"><a href="#Hyper-Xenon-一键移植脚本" class="headerlink" title="Hyper Xenon 一键移植脚本"></a>Hyper Xenon 一键移植脚本</h1><h2 id="备注"><a href="#备注" class="headerlink" title="备注"></a>备注</h2><p><strong>将需要移植的HyperOS文件置于</strong><br><strong>DNA_HyperSuper项目中，再进行分解</strong><br><strong>需分解product system system_ext mi_ext四个分区</strong><br><strong>新版NFC页面及MiBeam修改在vendor分区</strong></p>
<h2 id="Shell脚本"><a href="#Shell脚本" class="headerlink" title="Shell脚本"></a>Shell脚本</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/priv-app/MIUIBrowser/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/BaiduIME/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/iFlytekIME/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIGalleryLockscreen/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIService/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIUIEmail/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIUIHuanji/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIUIMiDrive/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/data-app/MIUIVirtualSim/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/app/HybridPlatform/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/app/MSA/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/app/AnalyticsCore/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/app/Updater/</span><br><span class="line">rm -r /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/app/MiTrustService/</span><br><span class="line">echo 精简完成</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 定义要添加的内容，每行内容用换行符\n分隔</span><br><span class="line">content=&quot;\n#Xtempest Xenon\n#flashh optimize\npersist.miui.density_v2=440\nro.sf.lcd_density=440\n#cores\npersist.sys.miui_animator_sched.bigcores=4-6\npersist.sys.miui_animator_sched.big_prime_cores=4-7\npersist.vendor.display.miui.composer_boost=4-7\n#prestrain\npersist.sys.prestart.proc=false\npersist.sys.preload.enable=false\n#threads\npersist.sys.miui_animator_sched.sched_threads=4\n#firstframe\npersist.sys.first.frame.accelerates=true\n#millet\npersist.sys.powmillet.enable=true\npersist.sys.brightmillet.enable=true\npersist.sys.millet.handshake=true\npersist.sys.millet.newversion=true\nro.millet.netlink=30\n#sf\nro.miui.surfaceflinger_affinity=\npersist.sys.miui.sf_cores=\nro.miui.affinity.sfui=4-6\nro.miui.affinity.sfre=4-6\nro.miui.affinity.sfuireset=4-6\n#camera\ncamera.lab.options=1\n#aptx\npersist.vendor.qcom.bluetooth.aptxadaptiver2_2_support=true\n#audio\nro.vendor.audio.sfx.harmankardon=true\nro.vendor.audio.spk.clean=true\n#haptic\nsys.haptic.slide_version=2.0\n#dis timeout\nro.vendor.display.type=\n#logd_off\nvendor.bluetooth.startbtlogger=false\npersist.sys.offlinelog.kernel=false\npersist.sys.offlinelog.logcat=false\npersist.sys.offlinelog.logcatkernel=false\nro.logdumpd.enabled=0\nro.logd.size.stats=4K\nro.lmk.debug=false\nro.kernel.android.checkjni=0\nro.kernel.checkjni=0\nsys.miui.ndcd=off\npersist.sys.offlinelog.logcat=false\npersist.sys.offlinelog.logcatkernel=false\npersist.sys.offlinelog.kernel=false\nvendor.bluetooth.startbtlogger=false\npersist.logd.limit=OFF\npersist.logd.size=65536\npersist.logd.size.crash=1M\npersist.logd.size.radio=1M\npersist.logd.size.system=1M\npersist.mm.enable.prefetch=false\nlog.tag.stats_log=OFF\nro.logd.size=64K\nro.logd.size.stats=64K\ndebug.sqlite.wal.syncmode=OFF\ndebug.sqlite.journalmode=OFF\n#bluetooth fix\nbluetooth.profile.bap.unicast.client.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.bap.broadcast.source.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.bap.broadcast.assist.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.ccp.server.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.csip.set_coordinator.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.hap.client.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.mcp.server.enabled=false\nbluetooth.profile.vcp.controller.enabled=false\n#Extra Edition\nro.vendor.build.security_patch=2024-09-05\nro.product.brand=Redmi\nro.product.manufacturer=Xiaomi\nro.product.model=23049RAD8C\nro.product.marketname=Redmi Note 12 Turbo\nro.miui.product.home=com.miui.home\ndebug.game.video.speed=true\ndebug.game.video.support=true\nro.product.extra.name=diting\n#marble port\npersist.sys.debug.enable_scout_memory_monitor=true\npersist.sys.debug.enable_scout_memory_resume=true\npersist.sys.debug.scout_memory_disable_kgsl=true\npersist.sys.scout_dumpbysocket=true\npersist.sys.scout_binder_gki=true\npersist.sys.device_config_gki=true\npersist.sys.mmms.lowmem.wmark.boost.factor=1\npersist.sys.mms.compact_enable=true\npersist.sys.spc.enabled=true\npersist.sys.spc.gamepay.protect.enabled=true\npersist.sys.use_mi_new_strategy=true\npersist.sys.mmms.switch=true\npersist.sys.mms.bg_apps_limit=96\npersist.sys.mmms.throttled.thread=8960\npersist.sys.spc.protect.critical.count=2\npersist.miui.miperf.enable=true\nro.miui.notch=1\npersist.miui.extm.enable=1\npersist.miui.extm.version=3.0\npersist.lm.em.per_flush_quota_low=20000\npersist.lm.em.per_flush_quota_medium=12000\npersist.lm.em.per_flush_quota_high=8000\npersist.lm.em.flush_zram_usedrate=30\npersist.em.low_flush_level=8\npersist.em.medium_flush_level=6\npersist.em.high_flush_level=4\npersist.sys.use_boot_compact=true\npersist.sys.stability.abreuse_status=on\npersist.sys.miui_animator_sched.bigcores=4-6\npersist.sys.miui_animator_sched.big_prime_cores=4-7\npersist.sys.enable_templimit=true\nro.vendor.radio.5g=3\nro.vendor.radio.features_common=3\nro.miui.vicegwsd=true\npersist.vendor.radio.enable_temp_dds=true\nro.vendor.radio.fastdormancy=true\nro.display.screen_type=1\npersist.sys.precache.enable=true\npersist.sys.precache.appstrs1=com.sina.weibo,com.ss.android.article.news,com.taobao.taobao,com.smile.gifmaker\npersist.sys.precache.appstrs2=com.ss.android.ugc.aweme,com.tencent.mm,tv.danmaku.bili\npersist.sys.powmillet.enable=true\npersist.sys.brightmillet.enable=true\npersist.sys.millet.handshake=true\npersist.sys.millet.newversion=true\nro.miui.cust_erofs=1\npersist.sys.smartpower.display.enable=true\npersist.sys.testTrimMemActivityBg.wk.enable=true\npersist.sys.extra_buffer_num=1\npersist.sys.memory_standard.enable=true\npersist.sys.expend_heap_size=268435456\npersist.sys.expend_min_ram_limit=4\npersist.sys.memory_standard.appheap.enable=true\npersist.sys.memory_standard.handle.time=300000\npersist.sys.smartpower.display_camera_fps_enable=true\nbluetooth.profile.asha.central.enabled=true\npersist.sys.adoptable=force_off\npersist.miui.extm.dm_opt.enable=true\n#Xenon Optimize\npersist.sys.background_blur_supported=true\npersist.sys.background_blur_status_default=true\npersist.sys.background_blur_mode=0\npersist.sys.background_blur_version=2\ninit.svc.fbo-installd=running\npersist.sys.stability.miui_fbo_enable=true\npersist.sys.fboservice.ctrl=true\ndebug.config.media.video.frc.support=true\ndebug.config.media.video.ais.support=true\ndebug.config.media.video.aie.support=true\nro.vendor.audio.game.effect=true\npersist.vendor.accelerate.charge=true&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 定义build.prop文件的路径</span><br><span class="line">file_path=&quot;/data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/mi_ext/etc/build.prop&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 使用echo和&gt;&gt;操作符将内容追加到文件末尾</span><br><span class="line">echo -e &quot;$content&quot; &gt;&gt; &quot;$file_path&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 输出成功信息</span><br><span class="line">echo &quot;内容已添加到/mi_ext/etc/build.prop文件中&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 处理system/</span><br><span class="line">cp -rf /data/DNA/需替换文件/system/* /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 处理product/</span><br><span class="line">cp -rf /data/DNA/需替换文件/product/* /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/product/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 处理system_ext/</span><br><span class="line">cp -rf /data/DNA/需替换文件/system_ext/* /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system_ext/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo 处理分区成功</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 关闭tango</span><br><span class="line"># 使用sed命令在指定行前添加#</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.enabled=1/#tango.enabled=1/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.debug=off/#tango.debug=off/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.pretrans.max_size=67108864/#tango.pretrans.max_size=67108864/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.pretrans_on_install=true/#tango.pretrans_on_install=true/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.pretrans.debug=off/#tango.pretrans.debug=off/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.pretrans.lib=true/#tango.pretrans.lib=true/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line">sed -i -e&#x27;s/^tango.pretrans.apk=true/#tango.pretrans.apk=true/&#x27; /data/DNA/DNA_HyperSuper/system/system/build.prop</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo 处理tango成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
